"title": "8107: assurance, and life of faith",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8107: assurance, and life of faith",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The completeness of conviction and confidence expressed in the life of the believer, worked by the Holy Spirit. It derives from a reliance upon God and his promises alone, and results in boldness and steadfastness in service and in the face of difficulties.</p>\n<h2>Assurance and faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:3\">DEU 9:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:21\">DEU 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:9\">JOS 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:17\">2CH 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:8\">JHN 17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:1\">HEB 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5\">HEB 12:5</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance and hope</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:11\">HEB 6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:18\">PRO 23:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:19\">HEB 6:19</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance expressed by believers</h2>\n<h3>Assurance in adversity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:6\">HEB 13:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:6-Ps118:7\">PSA 118:6–118:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:6\">PSA 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:3-Ps27:5\">PSA 27:3–27:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1-Ps46:3\">PSA 46:1–46:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:5-Ps71:6\">PSA 71:5–71:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:26\">PSA 73:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:16\">2CO 4:16</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of God's promises</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:14\">JOS 23:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:20-Rom4:21\">ROM 4:20–4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:20\">2CO 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance in ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16\">ROM 1:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:13\">1TI 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:4\">2CO 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:1\">2CO 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:14\">2CO 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:12\">2PE 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance in prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:14\">1JN 5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:21-1John3:22\">1JN 3:21–3:22</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:5\">ROM 14:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:14\">ROM 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:23\">ROM 14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:9-1Cor8:11\">1CO 8:9–8:11</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance may be strengthened</h2>\n<h3>Examples of believers asking for assurance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:8\">GEN 15:8</a> <em>Abraham</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:16\">EXO 33:16</a> <em>Moses</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:17\">JDG 6:17</a> <em>Gideon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:18\">LUK 1:18</a> <em>Zechariah</em></p>\n<h3>Assurance through understanding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Assurance through waiting on God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:10\">PSA 46:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:14\">PSA 27:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:20\">PSA 33:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:15\">ISA 30:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:17-Isa32:18\">ISA 32:17–32:18</a> <em>The revelation of God's righteousness among his people results in true peace.</em></p>\n<h3>Assurance strengthened by others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:6-2Chr32:8\">2CH 32:6–32:8</a> <em>by example</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14\">2TI 3:14</a> <em>through teaching</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">COL 4:12</a> <em>through prayer</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:2-1Thess3:3\">1TH 3:2–3:3</a> <em>through encouragement amidst trials</em></p>\n<h3>False teaching weakens assurance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:2\">2TH 2:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:18\">2TI 2:18</a></p>\n<h2>The delusion of false assurance</h2>\n<h3>The danger of self-assurance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:12\">2CO 10:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:3-Phil3:4\">PHP 3:3–3:4</a></p>\n<h3>Such assurance proved false by conduct</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:6\">1JN 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:9-1John2:11\">1JN 2:9–2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:6\">1JN 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:20\">1JN 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:9\">2JN 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:11\">3JN 1:11</a></p>",
